  • Constructor Details

    • Tram

      protected Tram​(int id, EventManager eventManager, TrafficManager trafficManager, int weight, int speed, java.lang.String tramType)
      Initializes a new Tram
      Parameters:
      id - the internal id of this tram
      eventManager - the eventManager used to communicate with the TrafficManager, must be non-null
      weight - the total weight of this tram excluding passengers in kg, must be a positive integer
      speed - the speed this tram will move at in km/h, must be a positive integer
      tramType - the type identifier of this tram, must be non-null and not empty
      Throws:
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if invalid arguments are passed
